1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e5 3. dxe5 Ng4 4. Nf3 Bc5 5. e3 Nc6 6. Nc3 O-O 7. Be2 Ngxe5
{ In the theoretical section, I recommended to always take with the c-Knight although it won't matter in this game. }
